summary: This document is a Google subscriber information record for an account associated with the email address 'xst@yahoo.com', created on September 5, 2007. It lists the Google services used and login history, and is part of the evidence production in the Epstein case, identified by SDNY and EFTA file numbers.

events.title: Google Account Creation
events.description: A Google account associated with the email address 'xst@yahoo.com' was created.

keyFacts: The document is a Google subscriber information record for an account linked to the email 'xst@yahoo.com'.
The account was created on September 5, 2007, and shows last logins in 2016, 2015, and 2014.
The record is part of produced evidence in the Epstein case, identified by file numbers EFTA_00118845, SDNY_GM_00004772, and EFTA01265486.
